    "In addition, scientists can collaborate with linguists to generate language models that are more linguistically and culturally sensitive.",
    "Lastly, another rather radical approach could be intoducing an artificial language into AI chatbot systems to cater to non-native English speakers, which could potentially help reduce inequality.",
